    This is a model class for Country object containing data members for storing, assigning and retrieving name, number, co-ordinates, armies and continents.

    This class manages the dice entity and data members for the roll activity in attack phase.
    Map
    This class parses the map file and create countries, territories, continents and neighboring countries.
    Player
    This is a model class for a Player with member variables for id, name, countries, armies assigned and cards collected
